<body>
    <h1>Handover from architect to designer</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 style=3D"text-align: left;" id=3D"Handoverfromarchitecttodesign=
er-"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-ma=
nual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail" dr=
aggable=3D"false" width=3D"250" src=3D"db3b4466cb8a69d908166aace4ff04526331=
3499ecdec26076a56330bae461c3" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments/12032=
79395/Picture1.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1663571087337&amp;api=
=3Dv2" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"12032=
79396" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"atta=
chment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"Picture1.png" data-base-url=
=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au" data-linked-resource-content-typ=
e=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1203279395" data-linke=
d-resource-container-version=3D"1" alt=3D"" height=3D"158"></span></h2>
<h2 style=3D"text-align: left;" id=3D"Handoverfromarchitecttodesigner-Archi=
tecttoDesigner">Architect to Designer</h2>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">A meeting should be scheduled for a formal h=
andover to be initiated. This meeting should provide a walk through by the =
architect of the high level use cases for the API for context what the API =
is intending to support and how it fits in the overall solution</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong=
>It is your responsibility to schedule a meeting with the architect <br></s=
trong></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">At a minimum the following pieces of =
information for the API must be provided in the meeting before a design of =
an API can begin:<br></span></p>
<ol>
<li>Endorsed API Name including basepath</li>
<li>Endorsed Resources and operations</li>
<li>Business Owner/Technical Owner/Support team details</li>
</ol>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">If SLA information is available, othe=
rwise default initially to the golden swagger specification</span></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
